Package com.mhealthatlas.apps.repository

com.mhealthatlas.apps.repository contains all repository interfaces of the application service.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AndroidAppRepository
    Contains methods to interact with the database.
    The query annotations uses the entity classes defined in AndroidApp.
    AndroidAppVersionRepository
    Contains methods to interact with the database.
    The query annotations uses the entity classes defined in AndroidAppVersion.
    AppVersionTaxonomyClassRepository
    Contains methods to interact with the database.
    The query annotations uses the entity classes defined in AppVersionTaxonomyClass.
    CategoryRepository
    Contains methods to interact with the database.
    The query annotations uses the entity classes defined in Category.
    IosAppRepository
    Contains methods to interact with the database.
    The query annotations uses the entity classes defined in IosApp.
    IosAppVersionRepository
    Contains methods to interact with the database.
    The query annotations uses the entity classes defined in IosAppVersion.
    MHealthAtlasAppRepository
    Contains methods to interact with the database.
    The query annotations uses the entity classes defined in MHealthAtlasApp.
    OutboxRepository
    Contains methods to interact with the database.
    The query annotations uses the entity classes defined in OutboxEntity.
    PrivateAppRepository
    Contains methods to interact with the database.
    The query annotations uses the entity classes defined in PrivateCustomerApp.
    PrivateAppVersionRepository
    Contains methods to interact with the database.
    The query annotations uses the entity classes defined in PrivateCustomerAppVersion.
    TaxonomyClassRepository
    Contains methods to interact with the database.
    The query annotations uses the entity classes defined in TaxonomyClass.
